{"tid":1651833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[請廣傳幫手]有無人影到今日兩點半班黑狗私家車用救護車開路直撞示威者既片?","createTime":"2019-10-13T13:02:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T13:38:57.000Z","uid":34816,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7a57d2a5b968bf45ed14947035aa6abacfd948f5","tid":1651833,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"為左捉人，班死仆街黑狗到左今時今日既戰術已經毫無底線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n話說今日兩點半左右，手足係荃灣新之城對出青山公路荃灣段set左rb，然後突然聽到前面位置有救護車聲，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">當車群讓路予救護車後，有數架私家狗車突然加速衝出直接衝開rb再不減速直接撞入示威人群到，速龍落車邊開槍邊拘捕</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於事出太突然真係無咩人影到相關片段，我跪求有影到既人士可唔可以拎出黎，一齊向傳媒國際線等煲大佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n手足你地以後set rb要set得厚d同實淨d，唔係班狗真係無性架，會直接撞過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋如非必要真係唔好再讓任何車輛通過。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌你班死黑狗你地死全家都唔撚夠還，有影到車牌既手足幫手上報果幾架仆街狗車，唔好以為唔撚洗還</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9ad2cb9d47cfff6950a60751165353036f7cde75","tid":1651833,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日咁樣捉左好多個啊，好多人真係驚到走唔切"},{"pid":"9546a7eb67aa36cb88543eec47d5f34dc9ad50dd","tid":1651833,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65e132c1ef8923bdb7b065077303eb98ee4ac12","tid":1651833,"uid":105976,"like":0,"disl